{"tid":419594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司機被截炫耀國際車牌 嘲警員唔識貨","createTime":"2017-09-30T15:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T07:59:39.000Z","uid":34252,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"34b37ffaf1f678878d9909334d379950d145ce00","tid":419594,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:29:55.000Z","msg":"做人不要太囂張！安徽當塗縣姑孰鎮一名姓汪男司機本月14日在路口因未禮讓行人，遭交通警截停，對方要求他出示駕駛執照，惟他囂張地拿出「國際車牌」，聲稱可在全球多個國家使用。交通警解釋內地不能使用國際車牌，汪男竟嘲笑其不識貨，還指自己只有一張駕照。<br />\n<br />\n該名警員隨後警告，若司機沒有內地駕照便算無牌駕駛，汪聽到「無牌駕駛」四字後，嚇得馬上拿出內地駕照，最後因未按規定禮讓行人，被罰款100元人民幣及扣3分。有網民指出，中國非國際車牌協議成員國，涉事司機拿的根本不是國際車牌，「什麼國際駕照，只是中國駕照的不同外文翻譯本罷了，裝什麼裝？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChiNa<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GiiJC5gMdKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGiiJC5gMdKI&d=vu6s8LH4hirWXswi0N35ysn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=04f5165b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GiiJC5gMdKI</a>"},{"pid":"2c425abfed1be1efb32a48c4237c2587c5e6fed8","tid":419594,"uid":34252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80d3fa178201444a99f103c8b9319a5b45a78f5","tid":419594,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:51:06.000Z","msg":"唔想理你"},{"pid":"a4484a32963e65e79ffb332a82e2ca1f334f3c64","tid":419594,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T18:54:23.000Z","msg":"wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f740b25aef80c556acd9ef5a7e67f375d7b8fb51","tid":419594,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T21:39:20.000Z","msg":"就算係真既國際牌又點，有乜好炫耀？"},{"pid":"569a78d921bdd42a404255448be9adde27ffab62","tid":419594,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T21:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算係真既國際牌又點，有乜好炫耀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肯比80蚊我都有喇"},{"pid":"d14d68604a623b9ac5ae9e2d780407ed53eadaa1","tid":419594,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T21:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算係真既國際牌又點，有乜好炫耀？</blockquote><br />\n大陸冇人有國際牌自己咪覺得好威威囉<br />\n其實好多大陸人上淘寶俾人呃係國際牌，D大陸人係唔會check 就信"},{"pid":"bbd83674d440f9b151945a80bbed564ec8c89a42","tid":419594,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:32:45.000Z","msg":"IAA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同KIDA一樣專比支狗拎黎呃外國人"},{"pid":"d14c8051f45ae67d38e3f782478cd8ede590dfce","tid":419594,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T00:46:19.000Z","msg":"去香港搵人搞係出到國際牌架，運輸署都係無幾耐前先ban左，但已經唔知批左幾多出去"},{"pid":"a67c8dfbd485e9f60c8c5a794de7cd935fb09eed","tid":419594,"uid":51183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去香港搵人搞係出到國際牌架，運輸署都係無幾耐前先ban左，但已經唔知批左幾多出去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家規定要有香港身份證先批國際牌<br />\n以前無都唔知批左幾多<br />\n應該係有外國投訴<br />\n記得之前日本講到明<br />\n中國護照+香港國際牌<br />\n都唔會租車比你"},{"pid":"0fb1f436b2b6ee9bdb5213e8e3c3eb2083f3c4d2","tid":419594,"uid":67283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T01:06:39.000Z","msg":"成條片又冇聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又冇個司機Show車牌出嚟個下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5c8fc5ff6837fa1d1fec5e73ac976ff365f6cc","tid":419594,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去香港搵人搞係出到國際牌架，運輸署都係無幾耐前先ban左，但已經唔知批左幾多出去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家規定要有香港身份證先批國際牌<br />\n以前無都唔知批左幾多<br />\n應該係有外國投訴<br />\n記得之前日本講到明<br />\n中國護照+香港國際牌<br />\n都唔會租車比你</blockquote><br />\n07年取消,IDP有效期得一年<br />\n之前申請過最多用到08年就收哂皮"},{"pid":"e2035db7686f18090ac30e05f0beb56cf894a88f","tid":419594,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"大把國家唔理國際車牌"},{"pid":"225afa9a5a1c979301a1